{"tid":1408833,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[東鐵線]我急不及待好想坐頭等翻工了","createTime":"2019-08-04T18:27:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T20:35:17.000Z","uid":156509,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0e399571aee61a32bcbd1dd4b45db5f36c1ba14d","tid":1408833,"uid":156509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:27:10.000Z","msg":"東鐵線頭等 比你Royal級翻工享受<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日8月5號由班黑衫慢慢逼普通等<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我呢啲上等人就<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">買張一個站嘅頭等單程車飛</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">嘆住冷氣坐頭等</span></span>慢慢翻工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反正張飛入閘後有150分鐘坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">過左150分鐘先會超時</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果過左150分鐘比查飛狗捉到會罰$500</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我就唔信班車會成兩個幾鐘都開唔到囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地慢慢逼普通等啦，我就去嘆頭等先喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fc0edd24af0edb73202de233e68274a10bf71d4","tid":1408833,"uid":156509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:27:32.000Z","msg":"哇屌咁都俾樓主諗到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓主英明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a0f3e2381ee8f5a6b97d13a3a18596f72d006fc","tid":1408833,"uid":156509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply